abstract: Yahoo wants to enlist a small army of search start-ups as allies in the hope that collectively they will be able to stop the Google juggernaut.
snippet: Yahoo wants to enlist a small army of search start-ups as allies in the hope that collectively they will be able to stop the Google juggernaut.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO  Unable to beat Google in the Web search business on its own, Yahoo is trying a new approach.

headline.main: Yahoo Is Inviting Partners to Build on Its Search Power
